title: Raw - La Suite West
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Raw, Western, British, English
description: Raw launched in 2013 within the La Suite West Hotel and is open to the public. This contemporary style restaurant removed meat from its menu became all-vegetarian in 2015. Breakfast is full English, continental, or a la carte. From lunchtime onward, the food is vegan with raw options. Serves mocktails, afternoon tea with choice of non-dairy milk. Location is next to the Kensington Gardens.
